s=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa935317aa17b4a79d2d79c3fea873aebc3ebe16","tid":425562,"uid":65643,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:31:40.000Z","msg":"一個月有乜問題<br />\n同你散完先開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4c0aa8d30cdc3c6b004b837eaed684f2f004ac","tid":425562,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:34:37.000Z","msg":"未同你完已經有啦傻仔"},{"pid":"27fefc4114c2192e7066eb649ab573dc351a2289","tid":425562,"uid":78559,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:35:46.000Z","msg":"分咗手先同人一齊嘅話<br />\n呢度已經冇你嘅事"},{"pid":"2500d36de68aa6b4c4080479596ddc93297e38d2","tid":425562,"uid":24513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:37:16.000Z","msg":"好多所謂&quot;散左之後先開始&quot;<br />\n其實之前未正式開始姐, 咪一樣因為有第2個先散<br />\n<br />\n利:2星期(so called)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22129f09972b337535d3205ae474c0010ae9d83e","tid":425562,"uid":41298,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:45:58.000Z","msg":"其實好多時唔係佢一路都唔愛你,而係分手嗰陣唔再愛你,所以先合理化自己正式同你分咗手先同第個一齊。<br />\n<br />\n個timeline應該係:好鐘意你&gt;發現你有缺點&gt;講過提過你又無乜改&gt;又發現你多個缺點&gt;廢撚事再重提&gt;慢慢失望/心淡&gt;慢慢放手&gt;被乘虛而入&gt;鐘意咗第個<br />\n<br />\n而你個timeline係:好鐘意佢&gt;發現佢有缺點,但係呢啲係磨合必經階段啦&gt;包容咗佢缺點&gt;以為佢都會咁包容你&gt;唔撚覺佢心淡你&gt;突然有一日被分手&gt;好快同第個一齊<br />\n<br />\n不過咁講,香港,勝在有厹<br />\n<br />\n利,過來人"},{"pid":"e5e9419a244ebe15ac61ed5b32d8119959bb0a8a","tid":425562,"uid":121754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:47:22.000Z","msg":"四日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5850b8b7d6aecfcabe8997931f9b4afc31316885","tid":425562,"uid":22256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:57:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實好多時唔係佢一路都唔愛你,而係分手嗰陣唔再愛你,所以先合理化自己正式同你分咗手先同第個一齊。<br />\n<br />\n個timeline應該係:好鐘意你&gt;發現你有缺點&gt;講過提過你又無乜改&gt;又發現你多個缺點&gt;廢撚事再重提&gt;慢慢失望/心淡&gt;慢慢放手&gt;被乘虛而入&gt;鐘意咗第個<br />\n<br />\n而你個timeline係:好鐘意佢&gt;發現佢有缺點,但係呢啲係磨合必經階段啦&gt;包容咗佢缺點&gt;以為佢都會咁包容你&gt;唔撚覺佢心淡你&gt;突然有一日被分手&gt;好快同第個一齊<br />\n<br />\n不過咁講,香港,勝在有厹<br />\n<br />\n利,過來人</blockquote><br />\n講得好啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 共勉之"},{"pid":"42f6fc0629e521bde0cba1d7852f9ea30947777e","tid":425562,"uid":282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:00:08.000Z","msg":"點睇我講完分手佢第2日就喺我面前拖另一條仔隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f435d02e733967b1c8110ac4be5877da674df4","tid":425562,"uid":150030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉個角度，其實女人攞嚟屌閪同含撚嘅動物，咁你會開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係開心左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33951ffc5a3489ad8b9a7a925f4b04334f25d226","tid":425562,"uid":70292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好過我阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我ex係1星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你係唔係戴咗綠帽自己唔知啊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能條女同時間溝緊幾個添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e19f002f75f1440d40dcb2c99278b5eaf989e0c","tid":425562,"uid":120317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:20:02.000Z","msg":"樓主咪算好<br />\n我初戀未分手就已經瞞住我同個呀叔拍拖仲要個呀叔本身有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過賤人會有報應，條八婆之後識親都係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次唔多過一個月貨仔。<br />\n佢老母同我講叫佢疊埋心水自己過埋下半世<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a909f8b6e32c21c0036dcb2c5ba49753d1c38078","tid":425562,"uid":22256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:53:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主咪算好<br />\n我初戀未分手就已經瞞住我同個呀叔拍拖仲要個呀叔本身有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過賤人會有報應，條八婆之後識親都係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次唔多過一個月貨仔。<br />\n佢老母同我講叫佢疊埋心水自己過埋下半世<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呀叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n他朝君體也相同<br />\n你宜家見到佢咁有咩諗法<br />\n<br />\n我嗰個都係初戀嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff6d2d42ef77ad5aaa894d5e2be27c98d0d28bf","tid":425562,"uid":22256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇我講完分手佢第2日就喺我面前拖另一條仔隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾耐嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838d7e06a37ffcbc8705bef0fbbe152bcbf77d18","tid":425562,"uid":72943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:56:42.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩 分左手啦"},{"pid":"3a0399294677d3ca7c4ebf711ab519da858ca880","tid":425562,"uid":94259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T02:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實好多時唔係佢一路都唔愛你,而係分手嗰陣唔再愛你,所以先合理化自己正式同你分咗手先同第個一齊。<br />\n<br />\n個timeline應該係:好鐘意你&gt;發現你有缺點&gt;講過提過你又無乜改&gt;又發現你多個缺點&gt;廢撚事再重提&gt;慢慢失望/心淡&gt;慢慢放手&gt;被乘虛而入&gt;鐘意咗第個<br />\n<br />\n而你個timeline係:好鐘意佢&gt;發現佢有缺點,但係呢啲係磨合必經階段啦&gt;包容咗佢缺點&gt;以為佢都會咁包容你&gt;唔撚覺佢心淡你&gt;突然有一日被分手&gt;好快同第個一齊<br />\n<br />\n不過咁講,香港,勝在有厹<br />\n<br />\n利,過來人</blockquote><br />\n仲要扮到好對唔住自己個個可憐樣真係好想一巴煎撚死佢"},{"pid":"ca906812f7bbd5efa0247b4b07f8ed5289a0a8c0","tid":425562,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T02:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7773e57c5f45afe6c974ec4427b8e875546d8f","tid":425562,"uid":48776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T02:35:56.000Z","msg":"條仔分左手3日有第二條女"},{"pid":"2b79ee0c4b6923cef498b60043aa8a8c11764498","tid":425562,"uid":136699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T03:24:46.000Z","msg":"四日咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f2af3a68a1984c35b4e850f20de4e61610a3b3","tid":425562,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T03:28:40.000Z","msg":"有晒計劃"},{"pid":"ded91fb66e273da15cdc20f5eb14176b641d5004","tid":425562,"uid":60151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T03:31:51.000Z","msg":"急住去比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n通常一齊得咁快都唔會有好結果<br />\n<br />\n條臭閪好快會有報應"},{"pid":"a4e3f62a93e73143c626b2507dcad7152174aee6","tid":425562,"uid":136699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T03:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好出奇咩傻仔，三萬蚊，過夜呀</blockquote><br />\n三十都俾多佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f267ca50e5a0339bde73c8d1ab24ba0ed04b4d2c","tid":425562,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T03:38:43.000Z","msg":"一日一個星期一個月有分別咩 。"},{"pid":"2c6b4ececb37043dbd4042a65d70f0a8609a89b3","tid":425562,"uid":93200,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T03:43:58.000Z","msg":"唔算快架啦 我被分手第2日 <br />\n用ig分身ac見到佢話同第二條仔一齊合照仲話一個月快樂 好愛佢 <br />\n屌諗起都傷9心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734927b0a1ed76a4eb7545875dffd52edb11b3c8","tid":425562,"uid":97526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci