 />\n我朋友都係一星期後同左第二條仔一齊<br />\n我地成班fd都有話過佢<br />\n但佢覺得自己冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328bab5189796ae5a81ca031ed603bd483998b71","tid":425562,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:21:06.000Z","msg":"怪得邊個"},{"pid":"49e37e53d5a48f5d7b29e1745f2608a583cb500a","tid":425562,"uid":30495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:21:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好過我阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我ex係1星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我朋友都係一星期後同左第二條仔一齊<br />\n我地成班fd都有話過佢<br />\n但佢覺得自己冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔通你朋友就係我ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e422a0d98ae7b6dd70d8c139496fadb68052461","tid":425562,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:22:28.000Z","msg":"同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇開了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c5baa4f69bcf79998148464ade8e7880ea757f","tid":425562,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://weknowmemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/end-of-a-relationship-men-vs-women.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweknowmemes.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F02%2Fend-of-a-relationship-men-vs-women.jpg&h=f9a6f1d7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}